you know, we have these security things that we're all care about, and we want to move those forward.

00:29:19.920 --> 00:29:22.959
And here's the value that you're getting personally that the business is getting.

00:29:24.319 --> 00:29:30.479
It helps you kind of make progress with this. The third one is to pair restrictions with power.

